Just a place to share some work on content.

To run examples with the accompanying data you must create a data base and change the appropriate fields
(database name, database user, database password) in the configuration.php.
These example require PHP 5.3.

These assume that you have a copy of the Joomla! Platform in a folder at the same level as the Content--Play folder.
If you want to try the content example you will need to get the veroion of the platform with the proposed JContent
libraries and related changes from the ebaySF repository at Github.
